8 August 2008Government will hold Cluster media briefings on the decisions taken at the recently held July Cabinet Lekgotla.The purpose of the July Cabinet Lekgotla was to conduct a mid-year review of the implementation of government s Programme of Action (PoA) and to adopt a Medium Term Strategic Framework (MTSF).The briefings will take place at the Union Buildings, Room 153 and Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town.There will be a video link-up at all briefings.Briefings schedule:Monday, 11 August 2008 10:00 11:30: Economic, Investment and Employment Cluster chaired by Minister Mpahlwa Venue: Room 153, Union Buildings, PretoriaNB: The Social, JCPS and IRPS Clusters are still to be confirmed.Enquiries Harold Maloka (Pretoria) Cell: 082 847 9799Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)